Hermes Skills (references only)
--------------------------------
The capability tree references skill files from the Hermes Agent project
(Apache 2.0 or MIT). These are not bundled in this package — they come
from your local ~/.hermes/skills/ installation.

Unlicensed Skills
-----------------
The tree_10000.yaml file references ~763 additional community skills that
are NOT bundled because they carry no explicit open-source license. Per
copyright law, unlicensed work is "all rights reserved" — you may use
them locally but should not redistribute them.

You can install them locally via:
  skill-retriever install from-dir <path to local copy of AgentSkillOS data>

Original Sources
----------------
The community skill corpus originates from the AgentSkillOS research paper
(arXiv 2603.02176) and the HuggingFace dataset NPULH/agentskillos-benchmark.
The HF dataset is available under research terms at:
  https://huggingface.co/datasets/NPULH/agentskillos-benchmark
